---
title: Quick Double Creamy Bacon & Tomato Orecchiette with Leek & Garlic Pangrattato
description: Brighten your day with yet another stunning pasta dish. There are so many flavours you can try, and this creamy tomato and bacon combo is a standout among them. Add some crunch with a garlicky pangrattato for a meal we can’t get enough of.
